
Congratulations for finding this page! The information below is both interesting and informative. 
 
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
 
- Mass Hysteria is when a group of people have mental contagion without real disease or threat. The dancing plague of the Middle Ages and the recent TickTock dancing challenges are two compelling examples. 
 
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_mass_hysteria_cases
 
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
  
- Rehypothecation is when banks use their clients collateral as their own. The IMF claims it played a large roll in the 2008 financial crisis perpetrated by the shadow banking system. 
 
https://www.imf.org/external/pubs/ft/wp/2010/wp10172.pdf
 
  
https://www.investopedia.com/news/how-commingling-and-rehypothecation-affect-bitcoin/
 
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
 
- Cyber Economy is a term coined in the seminal book "The Sovereign Individual". Insights from this book remain relevant for anyone interested in personal autonomy and independence in the 21st century and beyond. 
 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m7YJgj57Css
 
__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
  
- Water Futures are now being traded on the CME. This implies there will be continued shortages of water as California and the world experience droughts. 
  
https://global.wf.com/hub_article/california-water-futures/
  
https://www.aljazeera.com/gallery/2021/8/30/drying-euphrates-syria-disaster
 
